data.description: The Royal Gorge Ranch is a versatile rustic mountain property that was once part of the original old Royal Gorge Ranch, The ranch offers stunning 360 views of the Royal Gorge Bridge and surrounding majestic Rocky Mountains, adjoining thousands of BLM acres for hunting and other. The Ranch consists of 48+ fenced and cross fenced mountain acres. There is a 1857 sq ft comfortable, rustic ranch style home, with a covered front porch and a native rock fireplace. Other structures include a beautifully remodeled 552 sq ft guest cottage, horse/livestock barns and other outbuildings and corrals. There is an older modular on the property that could be replaced as there is water and septic to that location. There is a high producing well on the ranch that once served 5 homes. This lends to the possibility of a RV park, tiny home community, hunting camp, guest ranch, lodge or additional homes on the property. The ranch is located in game unit 58 and allows for Elk, Deer, Pronghorn, Black bear, Mountain lion and Turkey hunting.  This is a great opportunity to purchase a diverse mountain property adjoining public lands for hunting, horseback riding, hiking, fishing and other recreational activities. Along with income producing capabilities, a mountain retreat or primary residence ranch.
